{"tid":2160282,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民調：拜登支持率5成　領先特朗普9個百分點","createTime":"2020-08-16T23:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T23:52:39.000Z","uid":240256,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"94378ec4a3300f1b438fa05783e7d7e2216cfbea","tid":2160282,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T23:31:40.000Z","msg":"《美國全國廣播公司》和《華爾街日報》聯合進行的民調顯示，民主黨總統參選人拜登在全國的民望領先爭取連任的總統特朗普9個百分點，支持率達5成。<br />\n<br />\n受訪選民相信，拜登在對抗新型肺炎疫情、移民、醫療護理、種族關係和團結國家等不同問題上，都會比特朗普做得更好。超過6成國民認為，特朗普政府未能成功抗疫，只有五分一人相信美國經濟仍十分穩固。<br />\n<br />\n另外，民調亦顯示，拜登獲大部分少數族裔支持，其中黑人的支持率高達8成8。年齡18至34歲的選民中，有5成4支持拜登。特朗普的支持者大多數是白人、男性及無大學學位的白人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544047-20200817.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544047-20200817.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRsTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=a1291b85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544047-20200817.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=03736abf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544047-20200817.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"be5cc708b881e642ac9029e18d08b200b73f9084","tid":2160282,"uid":313615,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T23:32:47.000Z","msg":"民調希拉莉支持率高過川普"},{"pid":"bba3c6d755feb7431848166c7dd2c59833a0d04c","tid":2160282,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T23:34:03.000Z","msg":"不過今年反trump人士意志堅定一定去投，唔拉到5%內，很困難"},{"pid":"77b1deed388ae53c1492ab30a7ed6cffaa71f20c","tid":2160282,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T23:34:37.000Z","msg":"😭😭😭😭😭"},{"pid":"fb2e46751f4bd4b1fe6d3da498c0c7f6e7078428","tid":2160282,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T23:35:24.000Z","msg":"香港完了。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" c